# FastAPI CRM Prototype

A lightweight **one-page CRM-like web application** built with:

- **Backend:** FastAPI  
- **Database:** SQLite + SQLAlchemy ORM  
- **Templates:** Jinja2 + [HTMX](https://htmx.org/) + [Alpine.js](https://alpinejs.dev/)  
- **Styling:** [TailwindCSS](https://tailwindcss.com/) via CDN  
- **Scope:** Development prototype only (Customers, Events, Call Center, Alarms)

---

## üöÄ Features

- Customer and Event management  
- Call Center workflow simulation  
- Alarm system (linked to Customers & Events)  
- Interactive UI using HTMX + Alpine.js (no full-page reloads)  
- Simple, single-page design for rapid prototyping  

